entries.femaleVariant: I believe I have collected enough to try.
Excellent timing.
I will be "in touch."
I'm in.
Good. Now try to enter the warehouse.
How'd your recon go?
I will draw their attention away.
You have made a cock-up! Arasaka reinforcements are here!
Had it right. Got an access point to the security systems.
Excellent. I am also making progress.
Uhm, in the tunnel. Tighter than a wetsuit in here. Aw, reeks, too.
entries.maleVariant: Uhm, in the tunnel. It's tighter than a wetsuit in here. Reeks, too.

entries.femaleVariant: You will have fresh air once you reach the warehouse area.
Mhm, rather clever.
Climbed the pipe. About to go in.
All is good here, also. I just evaded a patrol.
You are an easy target when you step out.
You... You really…
Well, well. Your tricks can be useful. Bravo.
Very well. I have reached the roof.
I will be in their communication system soon.
Hah, even I see you now!
What? That I dropped him?
You are truly mad.
That's why I'm here.
That's how we dupe 'em in counterintel.
On site!
Yes, I heard!
You were to be quiet!
Things didn't go exactly as planned!
I will try to distract them. You run to the float!
The complex is well guarded, but we should manage.
The floats stand in the main warehouse. Your task is simple – to get inside.
Uh, how?
The more quiet, the better. But you are the thief. I will not question your skills.
Once there, you must locate the largest platform and infect its system.
Where're you gonna be?
I will create a diversion. They should not discover our intentions.
Do you know what Arasaka despises the most, confuses them? When communication fails, when they cannot talk to each other. They are first to cry, "Sabotage!"
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="混乱するなぁ" t="Pure chaos." b="" a=""/>
The diversionary action – that is mine to do.
